blog.name: switch842
blog.title: Stark Raving Sane
blog.description:
Fangirl. SciFi Geek. Shakespeare Nerd. Ravenclaw. Concert Whore. Love music and theater. And musical theater. Spamalot owns my soul. Something Rotten is the greatest musical to ever exist. Wanna be ballerina.

Supernatural. Cobra Kai. Legion. Suits. Hannibal. Billy Zabka. Darren Criss. Christian Kane. Colin Cunningham. Jared, Jensen & Misha. Mads Mikkelsen. Matt Bomer. Dan Stevens. Nyle DiMarco. Matchbox Twenty. Bastille. Walk the Moon. Mondo Cozmo. COIN. Alt-rock, basically. Movies. These are things I will squee over here.

Random thoughts that pop in my head, weird dreams, and pretty things live here, too.

Also, spoilerphobe. So, if you reblog spoilers I probably won't follow you back. Nothing personal, I just find I enjoy shows more when I don't know everything that's going to happen before the episode airs.

My ask is always open!

summary: David Tennant | C2E2 2019 I can’t believe we actually made it into this panel, but we did and OMG YAY! David was just so...
caption:
David Tennant | C2E2 2019

I can’t believe we actually made it into this panel, but we did and OMG YAY! David was just so amazing. I swear he was a puppy in a past life. 

There was this one hilarious thing where he thought Naperville was Neighborville (when you ask a question they ask you to introduce yourself and where you’re from) and he was just, “No. That’s made up!” and just sort of kept going with it. Then someone a few people later corrected him and, “Oh, OK. That makes sense. I’ll give you Naperville.”

And the Monster Coffee! They were apparently a sponsor of some sort so they had bottles out on stage for the guests if they wanted. David decided to try it. Took a drink and just pulled the worst face ever like it was the rankest thing he’d ever had. And then remembered this is being filmed and they’re a sponsor so took another sip and declared how delicious it was! So funny.

summary: Last night I had a dream where I defined my bisexuality as being able to be attracted to both Billie Piper and Jodie Whittaker...
body:
Last night I had a dream where I defined my bisexuality as being able to be attracted to both Billie Piper and Jodie Whittaker at the same time. Like not because I’m attracted to women, but that as what bisexuality is. Being attracted to Billie and Jodie.

Then I went on to add that there’s not just two sides to bisexuality, so of course, I’m also attracted to David Tennant. I said it should be obvious I am since he’s a woman.
